         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// I ask (sb.) friendly. | May he be ... friendly ... ///</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// Do ...! | You do not ... this <distinct type="ms_text">yak!sa</distinct>(?) down. They/he will die. He will starve.</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// They may not scold this <distinct type="ms_text">etâsi</distinct>. Do not (plant?/stake?) [wood] in the small enclosed field.</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// Do ...! Do not let ... <hi>(horizontal line)</hi></seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">/// On the 15<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> day of the 1<hi rend="superscript">st</hi> (month). Bù. /// ///</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
            <p><note corresp="#a4" type="philcomment">The text in this line is followed by a horizontal line.</note><note corresp="#a5" type="philcomment">布: Chinese signature <hi>bù</hi> 布 (literally “cloth”), compare <ref type="ms" target="txt:m-pklc_18"/>.</note></p>
